Class OASiblingHelperDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.object.OASiblingHelperDelegate

  • public class OASiblingHelperDelegate
extends java.lang.Object
    Find the closet siblings objects that need the same property loaded. Used by DS and CS to be able to get extra data per request to server/datasource, and increase performance.
    Author:
    vvia
